-- Ace Names Ex-Assistant Attorney General Wayland General Counsel
-- B y   M e g a n   H i c k e y
-- 2013-06-19T20:26:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-19/ace-names-ex-assistant-attorney-general-wayland-general-counsel.html
Ace Ltd., the Swiss insurer with
operations in more than 50 nations, appointed  Joseph Wayland  as
general counsel, reporting to Chief Executive Officer Evan Greenberg.  Wayland served with the U.S. Justice Department, first as
deputy assistant attorney general responsible for litigation for
the Antitrust Division and then as the acting assistant attorney
general in charge of the division, the Zurich-based insurer said
today in a statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Megan Hickey in New York at 
 mhickey18@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
